    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for someone looking for a functional daily driver. The exterior does show some signs of age, including a few minor dings and some paint fading on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows typical wear from regular use. It runs well and has been consistently maintained, though it may require some minor cosmetic attention or small repairs in the near future to keep it in peak shape.",
