    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class, maintained in pristine, showroom condition. Every detail reflects a standard of care that is increasingly rare in the pre-owned market. For the discerning enthusiast who demands excellence without compromise, this offering stands as an exemplary investment in performance and prestige.",
      "price": 48500.0,
